    • createEmployeeSugestion

      public javax.swing.DefaultComboBoxModel<Employee> createEmployeeSugestion​(Schedule schedule, int dayIndex)
      This method create list of employees suitable for a building at given day
      Parameters:
      schedule - is used to get building
      dayIndex - defines day for which must be the suggestion created This method splits employees into 8 different categories, filters out unsuitable emloyees, and Employees with Full and Half Employment type are priority. Types of employee splits based on :Employment type, City priority, Whether they currentli work in another city Every employee with fulfilled hours and emloyees with given building in block list are filtered out Suggested employees are sorted based on the work hours at current week
